      <title>独家：消息人士称，江森自控正在考虑出售 ADT 报警装置</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/johnson-controls-weighs-sale-adt-alarms-unit-sources-say-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名知情人士告诉路透社，江森自控国际公司正在考虑出售其 ADT 警报业务，以剥离一些非核心业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/johnson-controls-weighs-sale-adt-alarms-unit-sources-say-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:43:54 GMT</pubDate>
